{"tid":1733530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派司法覆核《禁蒙面法》成功　高院裁定《緊急法》違憲","createTime":"2019-11-18T06:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T06:23:09.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e58f71e0e063311a2df3ccb6204f68feef5847c","tid":1733530,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:22:31.000Z","msg":"民主派司法覆核《禁蒙面法》成功　高院裁定《緊急法》違憲<br />\n<br />\n2019/11/18 <br />\n<br />\n24 名民主派立法會議員及社民連梁國雄，早前分別入禀高等法院申請司法覆核，挑戰政府引用《緊急法》訂立《禁蒙面法》，<span style=\"color: red;\">高院法院今午頒佈裁決，裁定《緊急條例》就其賦權行政長官同行政會議，在任何危害公共安全的情況時訂立規例，並不符合《基本法》規定。<br />\n<br />\n法官又裁定，《禁蒙面規例》對基本權利所施加的限制超乎合理所需，並不符合相稱性驗證標準。</span>法庭將進一步聆訊讓與訟雙方就有關恰當濟助及訟費作陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n兩宗司法覆核案早前於高等法院合併審理，司法機構罕有地安排兩名法官周家明及林雲浩共同審理。代表申請人的名譽資深大律師陳文敏指，特首引用《緊急法》訂立《禁蒙面法》而不受任何制衡，但根據《香港人權法案條例》，當局須正式宣佈緊急狀態，才可採取措施，限制人權法案所賦予的權利和自由，質疑《禁蒙面法》涵蓋範圍過廣。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95-%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%2F&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2ZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=a293eacd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%2F&h=22e1210f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95-%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A/</a>"},{"pid":"ccbdb901309ac6ead167fe25c30d14f274dc9e2a","tid":1733530,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}